name: Michael Cannon
text: Steak sub was lite on the steak and super greasy. Role was cut through making it super hard to eat.  Wasn't busy so just expect more.

name: Jesse Kennedy
text: I hated it. I'm almost sick because the pizza is inedible. I got a BBQ chicken pizza with maybe 8 tiny pieces of chicken on it and smothered in BBQ to the point where I can't even take another bite. I'm not here to complain because I like â€¦More

name: Jo Baho
text: Papas has good food but minimum wage employees will only get you so far. Terrible service. Hire full time employees and pay them you cheap bastards.

name: Justin Auriemma
text: I eat lunch here alot and its always good but today the lady was beyond good she was sweet polite and delivered me a great lunch. And nothing beats getting in and out on a 30 min. Lunch break, thanks papa ginos cohasset.

name: Livingston Cheng
text: Courteous people, but the Supersteak just wasn't satisfying. Being from Philly, it's all about the bread/roll, and the rolls they use are just not good. Did enjoy the $1 slice special they had during lunch.

name: Cassie T
text: Usually when I order I like to avoid having bugs in my food. And the ace customer service of not responding when you point out that there was one is just fantastic.

name: sweed762
text: never gotten a bad pizza here & when we get delivery it's always on time & hot

name: Jake Wilson
text: Order this if you're prepared to wait two hours after the delivery time
